high_descs: Turn around, move around the island to the right, move to the sink, turn left, go to the sponge on the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn around, move forward, bring the sponge to the fridge on the left.
Put the sponge in the pot in the fridge.
Pick up the pot with sponge in the fridge.
Bring the pot with sponge to the sink on the left.
Put the pot with sponge in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with sponge in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go around the kitchen island to the counter on the right of the stove.
Pick up the green sponge on the right side on the top of the counter.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the green sponge inside the pot in the refrigerator.
Pick up the pot with the green sponge in it.
Turn left to go the front of the sink.
Place the pot with the green sponge inside into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move the pot with the green sponge from the refrigerator to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right to go around the kitchen island, then go forward and turn left at the sink.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn around, go forward until you reach the fridge then turn left.
Open the fridge and put the sponge in the pot, in the fridge.
Take the pot from the fridge.
Turn left and go forward to the end of the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the pot in the center of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a sponge in it in the sink.
